nodes.text: Shelby Young (born April 8, 1992) is an American actress who voices Princess Leia and Kneesaa in Star Wars: Forces of Destiny. She also voices multiple characters in Star Wars: Galaxy's Edge. Young later provided additional voices in the second season of The Mandalorian as well as Captain Bragg in The Bad Batch.
